Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.80,0:00:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fixture begins with a clear voice and enough silence for the detector to settle.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.70,0:00:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each caption line uses ordinary words so subtitle synchronization can focus on timing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.14,0:00:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third sentence is intentionally longer and gives the alignment code a wider speech island.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.23,0:00:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a pause the speaker continues with another compact sentence for the next cue.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.63,0:00:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A reliable fixture needs variation in length without becoming a long audiobook.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.24,0:00:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cue mentions video containers audio codecs and subtitle rewrites in plain language.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.84,0:00:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next phrase arrives after silence so the voice activity detector can split the span.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.69,0:00:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Short captions still matter because real subtitle files often mix brief and longer lines.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.97,0:01:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another sentence adds more timing evidence before the final codec cases begin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.53,0:01:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Near the end we keep the same calm delivery and leave room for timing drift checks.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.94,0:01:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One more cue gives the stretch test a broader timeline across the fixture.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.11,0:01:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final spoken cue closes the fixture with a simple sentence and a clean ending.
